{"tid":401174,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國要求英國勿再發表《香港半年報告書》","createTime":"2017-09-15T11:46:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-15T11:52:41.000Z","uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3b18500d236367611d543c98758177cde07aff1d","tid":401174,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T11:46:49.000Z","msg":"中國要求英國勿再發表《香港半年報告書》<br />\n<br />\n英國政府向國會提交最新一份《香港半年報告書》。在北京，外交部發言人華春瑩表示，香港回歸後的事務屬中國內政，外國無權干預，要求英方不要發表有關報告，停止干預香港事務。<br />\n<br />\n華春瑩說，香港回歸20年，繼續保持繁榮穩定，「一國兩制」實踐取得了舉世公認的成功。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1354269-20170915.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1354269-20170915.htm&d=apf0FnxfsF5SIMz8X09L8gHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=7ef2ddeb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1354269-20170915.htm&h=23ed09f6\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1354269-20170915.htm</a>"},{"pid":"9356ba35c0c8c06dd85c86d309bf9ea1d0a21cea","tid":401174,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T11:52:41.000Z","msg":"唔通唔發報告書，就等於本港永遠有「高品質管治」？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗起強國曾經出現過「國家免檢產品」認證 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}